# SENIOR FULLSTACK ENGINEER (3000-4000USD, Hochiminh City)- Vietnamese Candidates only

## DESCRIPTION

We are currently seeking a highly skilled and experienced Senior full-stack developer to join our dynamic team and lead the development of our web-based B2B2C marketplace platform.

## RESPONSIBILITIES

- Hands-on development of features
- Work closely cross-functionally: product, design, and business strategy
- Lead a team of developers through the product life cycle - architecture, design, development, quality, and production

## QUALIFICATION

- 7 years of experience in full-stack development, including minimum 2 years in front-end experience.
- At least 2 years of leadership experience for a lead-level position.
- Strong knowledge of the JVM, Java framework, Spring, Hibernate, and elects of the Java ecosystem.
- Understanding of common database design patterns and low-level behaviors of RDBMS.
- Understanding and experience in web performance measurement, analysis, and optimization.
- Understanding of the technical features of global services.
- Experience with frontend frameworks (React, Vue, or Angular).
- Experience in designing AWS-based services.
- Development experience in a Docker/Kubernetes environment.
- High standards for code quality, testing, and performance.
- At least 2 years of leadership experience for a lead level.
- Interested in new and emerging technologies and trends.
- Excellent collaboration and communication skills.

## WORKING HOUR

- Five-day work week 09:00 am to 06:00 pm

